version_description: This version is based on a good quality version but has added the complete song with detail not in any of the other versions. It is as close to perfect as it gets and as it sits is helpful when using your scrolling feature.
This is the admins version. Its for tab of the day.
I combined chords and tabs, corrected and improved them and make it all simple to read and play.
Has the passing chords included, has the correct Chorus chords and correct lyrics.
